The paper deals with optimization of wireless video communication systems, which involves information theory (cs.IT), multimedia (cs.MM), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper proposes a novel dual decomposition approach to decouple the users' decisions and determine foresighted policies, which involves optimization and control theory. The paper also mentions online learning, which is a common topic in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.IT, cs.MM, and cs.NI, followed by cs.SY and cs.LG.
